</b></p>
<p>73. The Working Group sent one case under its urgent action procedure to the 
Government. The case concerned Mr. <b>Mohammad Chowdhury Alam</b>, who was allegedly 
abducted in Dhaka by about seven law enforcement officers in civilian clothing on 25 June 
2010. The Government acknowledged receipt of this case. 
</p>
