</i></p>
<p><b>  Standard procedures 
</b></p>
<p>392. The Working Group transmitted one newly reported case to the Government. The 
case concerned Mr. <b>Nasrodin Guiamalon</b>, who was allegedly arrested at his home, located 
in Mindanao, by members of the 40th Infantry Battalion of the Philippines Army on 18 
March 2009.  
</p>
